{"body": "Hi all, if you want to use the `--editor` option in your Rails 3 app, you can run this command from your app directory:\r\n\r\n    curl https://gist.github.com/raw/4342095/rails -o script/rails\r\n\r\n(Since Rails 3 isn't accepting new features.)\r\n\r\nSee [my blog post](http://madebynathan.com/2012/12/19/open-files-generated-by-rails-generate-in-your-editor/) if you want to use it globally for all Rails 3 apps.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/11556942", "created_at": "2012-12-20T01:35:45Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5829#issuecomment-11556942", "updated_at": "2012-12-20T01:35:45Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5829, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/ndbroadbent", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/4931eceec58528529fd004e56af197c4?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6c444601992735a1c059ce1fdf1d4587.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/received_events", "gravatar_id": "4931eceec58528529fd004e56af197c4", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "ndbroadbent", "type": "User", "id": 139536, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ndbroadbent/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238126abd3543c15100d969"}, "id": 11556942, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5829"}
